KUSHAYISE abaningi ngovalo ukuzamazama umhlaba eThekiwini nezindawo ezakhelene naleli dolobha KwaZulu-Natal ngoLwesine. Ngemuva kuka- 1pm ngoLwesine emini, izakhamizi ezisedolobheni iTheku namaphethelo zifudukele ezinkundleni zokuxhumana zikhuluma ngokuzamazama komhlaba okuthuse abaningi kuleli. Ukuzamazama komhlaba kuthathe imizuzwana engu-42. Abantu abahlala eMkhomazi, Mgungundlovu, Hillcrest, Morningside naseDurban North bonke bakhale ngokuzamazama komhlaba. ULyse Comins ohlala eSouth Coast uthe ubehamba noyise beya kudokotela ngenkathi ezwa umsindo womhlaba uzamazama. “Ngisebenza eJacobs, eNingizimu yeTheku kodwa ngizwile umhlaba uzamazama,” kuchaza omunye umhlali. Omunye umhlali uthe ubesekhaya kubo ngenkathi ezwa indlu inyakaza. “Bekusabisa kakhulu,” kusho unina wezingane ezimbili. Kusolwa ukuthi lesi sehlakalo sihlobene nesibhicongo sokuzamazama komhlaba esenzeke esiqhingini saseMindanao ekuqaleni kwesonto. Ukuzamazama komhlaba, okube wu-6.5 magnitude, kudlule nezimpilo zabantu abayisithupha eMindanao. Baphawule kanje abantu ezinkundleni zokuxhumana: Guys relax it was just kaizer chiefs landing in Durban #earthquake pic.twitter.com/v08zVeBFeq Even the earth is complaining, we need jobs, our economy is falling I. To depression and the youth is losing hope! @CyrilRamaphosa you need to fix this before Mother Earth get extremely furious😡😡#tremor #earthquake A tremor in Durban? 😱 I hope everyone is safe. 🙏#tremor#earthquake A tremor in Durban? 😱 I hope everyone is safe. 🙏#tremor#earthquake #Earthquake or #Tremor in Durban. That was so scary 🙆‍♂️🙆‍♂️what the fuck 😂😂😂 Damn!! I'm still shaking. pic.twitter.com/LPEgRRnOnL